{"_id":"59e933e6ec54c9ad","name":"Control Spire Fragment","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"supply","target":"both","timing":"basic-action","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only — found near destroyed Control Spires"},"quantity":1,"effect":"Once per encounter as a Basic Action, place this fragment within 2 spaces. Until the start of your next turn all Digimon within 3 spaces of the fragment — ally and enemy alike — cannot digivolve or dedigivolve. The fragment crumbles after use.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Single use. Affects allies and enemies. Lasts until start of your next turn."}}
{"_id":"0623e74c73411442","name":"D-3 Digivice","type":"gear","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"itemType":"digivice","target":"tamer","timing":"passive","cost":{"digidollars":0,"realMoney":0,"special":"Loot only — cannot be purchased"},"quantity":1,"effect":"Must be equipped to digivolve your partner. Required to use Digi-Eggs — without the D-3 a Tamer cannot initiate Armor Digivolution even if they possess a Digi-Egg. Glows when wild or hostile Digimon are within 6 spaces. As a Free Action, scan one visible enemy to learn their Attribute and Element. As a Basic Action, perform a deep scan on one visible enemy to learn their Attribute, Element, and one combat stat of your choice. The D-3 supports digivolution up to Mega stage — it does not have the Ultimate cap of the Season 1 Digivice.","isEquipped":false,"bonuses":{"courage":0,"friendship":0,"love":0,"knowledge":0,"sincerity":0,"reliability":0,"hope":0,"hpDamageReduction":0,"attackBonus":0,"damageBonus":0,"skillBonuses":{"blitz":0,"ironclad":0,"crusher":0,"ghost":0,"roar":0,"scan":0,"rally":0,"broadcast":0,"mend":0,"radar":0,"tame":0,"decode":0,"jackIn":0,"modify":0,"trace":0,"archive":0,"command":0,"playback":0,"firewall":0,"reinforce":0,"coreDrive":0,"zeroError":0,"fieldOps":0,"recovery":0}},"notes":"Replaces Season 1 Digivice. Required for Armor Digivolution. Cap: Mega."}}
